    <p style="margin: 0; line-height: 1.6; color: var(--foreground);">
      LED transparent backboard neon signs are a solid mid-range choice for bedroom and dorm wall decor. At $49–57, they deliver the floating-neon aesthetic at a fraction of custom neon costs ($100–300+). The 500,000-hour lifespan means you'll never worry about burnout. USB-powered, no electrician needed. However, you get only 3 preset styles—zero customization. If you love one of the 3 designs and want plug-and-play ambiance, it's a hidden gem. If you need a specific custom design, keep shopping.
    </p>
  </div>

