  <!-- §11 How to Use -->
  <h2 style="font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">How to Install and Use This LED Neon Sign</h2>
  <div style="margin-bottom: 2.5rem;">
    <div style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
      <strong style="display: block; color: var(--primary); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Step 1: Mount the Sign</strong>
      <p style="margin: 0; line-height: 1.6;">
        Choose your wall location. The sign comes with adhesive strips or wall anchors. If using adhesive strips, clean the wall first (isopropyl alcohol works well). Press the sign firmly in place and let the adhesive set for 24 hours before plugging in. If using wall anchors, drill small holes, insert anchors, and screw the sign to the wall.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
      <strong style="display: block; color: var(--primary); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Step 2: Connect USB Power</strong>
